Class AbstractTemplateSqlTypeDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.type.descriptor.sql.spi.AbstractTemplateSqlTypeDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, SqlTypeDescriptor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractHANADialect.HANABlobTypeDescriptor, BigIntSqlDescriptor, BitSqlDescriptor, BlobSqlDescriptor, BooleanSqlDescriptor, ClobSqlDescriptor, DateSqlDescriptor, DecimalSqlDescriptor, DoubleSqlDescriptor, IntegerSqlDescriptor, NClobSqlDescriptor, NVarcharSqlDescriptor, RealSqlDescriptor, SmallIntSqlDescriptor, SqlTypeDescriptorRegistry.ObjectSqlTypeDescriptor, TimeSqlDescriptor, TimestampSqlDescriptor, TinyIntSqlDescriptor, VarbinarySqlDescriptor, VarcharSqlDescriptor

    public abstract class AbstractTemplateSqlTypeDescriptor
extends Object
implements SqlTypeDescriptor
    Abstract SqlTypeDescriptor that defines templated support for handling JdbcValueMapper resolution.
    See Also:

      • getSqlExpressableType

        public final SqlExpressableType getSqlExpressableType(BasicJavaDescriptor javaTypeDescriptor,
                                                      TypeConfiguration typeConfiguration)
        Delegates to TypeConfiguration.resolveSqlExpressableType(org.hibernate.type.descriptor.sql.spi.SqlTypeDescriptor, org.hibernate.type.descriptor.java.spi.BasicJavaDescriptor, java.util.function.Function<org.hibernate.type.descriptor.java.spi.BasicJavaDescriptor, org.hibernate.sql.SqlExpressableType>)
        "Implementation Requirements:"
        Defined as final since the whole point of this base class is to support this method via templating. Subclasses should instead implement createBinder(org.hibernate.type.descriptor.java.spi.BasicJavaDescriptor<X>, org.hibernate.type.spi.TypeConfiguration) and createExtractor(org.hibernate.type.descriptor.java.spi.BasicJavaDescriptor<X>, org.hibernate.type.spi.TypeConfiguration).

      • createBinder

        protected abstract <X> JdbcValueBinder<X> createBinder(BasicJavaDescriptor<X> javaTypeDescriptor,
